{"tid":2429721,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人最近啱啱喺外國帶貓返香港？","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:40:03.000Z","uid":281641,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"900a81344674afef903b94927647452a0dc052da","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"因為有啲事，黎緊要帶2隻貓返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知道如果喺美國返香港啲流程大概係點搞？<br />\n<br />\n點樣搞機票啲野？到左香港之後我要隔離的話2隻貓點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2fedcb8da5b603416f6a4c2e1815189c09d3e7","tid":2429721,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"香港呢邊唔知呢個關唔關事, 你可以望望, 美國果邊都可能有相關出口申請要做, 你quarantine緊果陣可能要問問係咪由AFCD養住佢地先定點, 唔知你呢邊有冇人會幫你手早D領回佢地<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fquarantine%2Fqua_ie%2Fqua_ie_ipab%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc.html&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=bff8db44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb030d461c7522a83aba4be10da44f8a79099f97","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b2fedcb8da5b603416f6a4c2e1815189c09d3e7","tid":2429721,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"香港呢邊唔知呢個關唔關事, 你可以望望, 美國果邊都可能有相關出口申請要做, 你quarantine緊果陣可能要問問係咪由AFCD養住佢地先定點, 唔知你呢邊有冇人會幫你手早D領回佢地<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fquarantine%2Fqua_ie%2Fqua_ie_ipab%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc.html&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=bff8db44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:51:56.000Z","msg":"屋企人可以接佢哋嘅<br />\n其實網上可以睇嘅文章同相關資料我都睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個心仲有啲十五十六唔知點所以想睇下有冇人最近帶過寵物返去可以圍爐問下細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da15380f411d04ef69ee2a1f1187acffba455606","tid":2429721,"uid":311792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"你要去漁農處整張簽證（大概兩個禮拜有得拎）$432<br />\n<br />\n美國屬於第二組別（可以去漁農處個網站度睇返隻貓需要打啲咩針先可以返嚟）<br />\n<br />\n同埋你返香港唔可以同隻貓一齊隔離（到時你要搵屋企人幫你去接隻貓，如果你揀國泰嘅話就要去國泰航空貨運站接）<br />\n<br />\n屋企人幫你去接貓嗰陣記得要打電話去Book，嗰陣佢話我冇打電話，就等咗好耐，因為你接完隻貓仲要等醫生check有冇問題，Check完仲要同隻貓過海關。"},{"pid":"9ddf7bbc645fa84d01e4358c3696b66a0573f050","tid":2429721,"uid":311792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b2fedcb8da5b603416f6a4c2e1815189c09d3e7","tid":2429721,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"香港呢邊唔知呢個關唔關事, 你可以望望, 美國果邊都可能有相關出口申請要做, 你quarantine緊果陣可能要問問係咪由AFCD養住佢地先定點, 唔知你呢邊有冇人會幫你手早D領回佢地<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fquarantine%2Fqua_ie%2Fqua_ie_ipab%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc.html&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=bff8db44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:01:32.000Z","msg":"講漏左<br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企人幫你接隻貓嘅話，嗰張簽證要寫埋代理人。"},{"pid":"9cac7a2ca905e8ea8fdd74679d7fe907e3a42015","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddf7bbc645fa84d01e4358c3696b66a0573f050","tid":2429721,"uid":311792