.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:01:32.000Z","msg":"講漏左<br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企人幫你接隻貓嘅話，嗰張簽證要寫埋代理人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔該！ 呢個我有諗過但係個網搵唔到點寫代理人！<br />\n<br />\n我一陣再望下張form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"你有唔明都可以問，有fd又係美國上個月帶左隻貓返黎，代理人就寫左我名，所以都大概知啲程序係點。<br />\n<br />\nbtw漁農處宜家大部分時間都home office，如果屋企人幫你整簽證要叫佢地睇清楚啲時間！"},{"pid":"8eb17b8282ae0855f5182f40d47372e3d53fbeef","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f6d7729fc64217d0c869f7451536fabc4efa04","tid":2429721,"uid":311792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cac7a2ca905e8ea8fdd74679d7fe907e3a42015","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddf7bbc645fa84d01e4358c3696b66a0573f050","tid":2429721,"uid":311792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:01:32.000Z","msg":"講漏左<br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企人幫你接隻貓嘅話，嗰張簽證要寫埋代理人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔該！ 呢個我有諗過但係個網搵唔到點寫代理人！<br />\n<br />\n我一陣再望下張form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"你有唔明都可以問，有fd又係美國上個月帶左隻貓返黎，代理人就寫左我名，所以都大概知啲程序係點。<br />\n<br />\nbtw漁農處宜家大部分時間都home office，如果屋企人幫你整簽證要叫佢地睇清楚啲時間！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得揀都唔想呢個時勢返嚟，但係偏偏屋企出咗事逼住要返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓你個frd係用邊隻貓籠？我上網見到好多都話可以用，但係覺得好唔穩陣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLwRtrk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLwRtrk.png&h=f46921c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇都係覺得呢隻穩陣啲<br />\n<br />\n另外你個friend帶隻貓返嚟有冇做blood test? 測體內狂犬病疫苗濃度嗰個，我見USDA同漁護處都冇話要，但係又好多人都話要做"},{"pid":"a13336e52d8fb1bccdad7a15b5d88af29543f129","tid":2429721,"uid":184507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900a81344674afef903b94927647452a0dc052da","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"因為有啲事，黎緊要帶2隻貓返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知道如果喺美國返香港啲流程大概係點搞？<br />\n<br />\n點樣搞機票啲野？到左香港之後我要隔離的話2隻貓點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"基本上你email Airline 佢會教晒你做所有野<br />\n香港呢邊黎打去AFCD都會教你逐步點做<br />\n<br />\n留意番，因為搞health certificate時間上好趕，嗰幾日會好忙<br />\n<br />\n你要隻貓搭飛機前14日內去獸醫嗰度做health certificate <br />\n然後拎Health Certificate去USDA APHIS Services Endorsement Office 做簽名同蓋印<br />\n<br />\n但USDA Endorsement Office依加因為COVID 非常有限度工作<br />\n佢話就話可以上網交啲文件 (要註冊獸醫做)，但個System係廢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己係親身去佢個office度交所有野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己早排都帶左隻狗由美國返香港，有咩唔明可以再問我"},{"pid":"a98ad1e64c37927999f41478cdc20701573c1cac","tid":2429721,"uid":184507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eb17b8282ae0855f5182f40d47372e3d53fbeef","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f6d7729fc64217d0c869f7451536fabc4efa04","tid":2429721,"uid":311792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cac7a2ca905e8ea8fdd74679d7fe907e3a42015","tid":2429721,"uid":281641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔該！ 呢個我有諗過但係個網搵唔到點寫代理人！<br />\n<br />\n我一陣再望下張form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"你有唔明都可以問，有fd又係美國上個月帶左隻貓返黎，代理人就寫左我名，所以都大概知啲程序係點。<br />\n<br />\nbtw漁農處宜家大部分時間都home office，如果屋企人幫你整簽證要叫佢地睇清楚啲時間！"},"cit